dct_description_sm: This flat map, prepared in July of 2019 by Data You Can Use, compares the percent of city-owned and bank-owned foreclosures in 2012 and 2017 for the City of Milwaukee. The map utilizes data from the City's Master Property File and 2010 Census tracts. For more information, please visit
